method/field via dot:
  (((`.` X f)))
  (((`.` (`.` X f) g)))
  (((`.` X 1)))
method via caret (passes through Symta's value lookup):
  (((`^` X f)))
arrow:
  (((`->` X f)))
function call:
  (((`()` f X)))
  (((`()` f X Y)))
  (((`()` f X Y Z)))
chained call + method:
  (((`.` (`()` f X) g)))
  (((`()` (`.` X f) Y)))
bracket index:
  (((`[` Xs 0)))
  (((`.` (`[` Xs Y) f)))
curly map:
  (((`{}` Xs (`*` `?` 2))))
list-literal vs method-call disambiguation:
  ((Xs (`[]` 1 2)))
  (((`.` Xs tail)))
